{
  "stem": "3631.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He gave him a-- a suit, one of his own suits.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He had him change right in his office there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He had a-- he carried his old uniform in a bundle.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And-- and he-- he sent him back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We didn't know his name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Later on, we found the building was in a-- in the chamber of commerce building.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's how the Czech people were.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They would stop us on the street-- we were walking around in uniform-- we looked in a pastry shop, and they come, which one do you like?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They went in and bought it for us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Or they brought us some-- some food.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we spent quarters, what we had in quarters, first in a-- first, I think, first [INAUDIBLE] we spent in a movie house that was open at night.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Prague was a very busy place, because there were people from all over Europe trying to get home-- a lot of Italians, a lot of Yugoslavs.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was-- it was a big-- big mess.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everybody was around and looking for-- looking for family, and so on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then, we were in a-- a-- I don't know where we were, somewhere.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We stayed in several places.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think we got some money for food from the-- from the Prague-- we had to register there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And but people-- young people walked around all over.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, they saw us, where were you?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Have you seen my brother?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My uncle, or my father?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They searched for people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when they saw my parents, and they saw-- saw my parent-- my mother, white-haired, and in her 50s, my-- my father, you know, white-hair and elderly-- for that time was an elderly gentleman-- they said, how come your parents are alive, and my parents are not alive?",
      "word_count": 48
    }
  ],
